    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/9d2295bfd15d069331b511dafefe0e56.poster.avif?t=1722268516\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/9d2295bfd15d069331b511dafefe0e56.webm?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/9d2295bfd15d069331b511dafefe0e56.mp4?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Digital Meow</strong> 是一款引人入胜的平台游戏，灵感来自旧操作系统和数字艺术的氛围。沉浸在一只小猫穿越数字世界寻找新家的故事中。遇到危险的陷阱，如激光、尖刺、大炮等。但小猫的意志坚定不移——在 Digital Meow 中一起克服这些具有挑战性的障碍！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/6bf8cf1fd70af5fa80f8428f317188fb.poster.avif?t=1722268516\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/6bf8cf1fd70af5fa80f8428f317188fb.webm?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/6bf8cf1fd70af5fa80f8428f317188fb.mp4?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点:</h2></strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >蒸汽波美学:</h2>享受一种独特的视觉风格，将旧操作系统的怀旧感与现代数字艺术相结合，营造出引人入胜的沉浸式环境。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有挑战性的游戏玩法:</h2>穿越各种危险的陷阱，包括激光、尖刺和大炮，需要精确的时机和快速的反应才能克服。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的故事:</h2>跟随一只寻找新家的小猫的感人故事，为游戏体验增添情感深度和动力。<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创新的关卡设计:</h2>探索创意设计的关卡，挑战您的平台技能，并在每个转弯处通过新的令人兴奋的障碍让您保持参与感。<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/d8b3edd60168dfa981f7aeb6e1ba1c8c.poster.avif?t=1722268516\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/d8b3edd60168dfa981f7aeb6e1ba1c8c.webm?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015130/extras/d8b3edd60168dfa981f7aeb6e1ba1c8c.mp4?t=1722268516\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></ul></li></ul>",
